1. Verify local repo config:
   ```bash
   git config user.email   # must be chauhangaurav101@gmail.com
   git remote get-url origin   # must contain github.com-personal:gachn/
   ```
2. If `user.email` is a Freshworks address, set local config:
   ```bash
   git config user.name "Gaurav Chauhan"
   git config user.email "chauhangaurav101@gmail.com"
   ```
3. Do **not** change global git config — only this repo's local config.
